<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
      .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
      .button { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; margin: 20px 0; }
      .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>ðŸŽ‰ Welcome to Magebase!</h1>
        <p>Your account has been created successfully</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello <%= @user.name %>!</h2>

        <p>Thank you for choosing Magebase! Your account has been created and is ready to use.</p>

        <p>Click the button below to sign in to your new account:</p>

        <%= link_to 'Access Your Account', @magic_link_url, class: 'button' %>

        <p><strong>This link will expire in 24 hours</strong> for your security.</p>

        <p>Once you sign in, you can:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>View your project proposals</li>
          <li>Track project progress</li>
          <li>Access your dashboard</li>
          <li>Set up a permanent password</li>
        </ul>

        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us.</p>

        <div class="footer">
          <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@magebase.site">hello@magebase.site</a></p>
          <p>&copy; 2025 Magebase. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>